📌 Numbered Steps (from the bottom of the slide)

🔹 Japanese:

① 成立確定待ちになったその日の夜間に成立（休日オンラインがある週は金土に成立確定待ちとなった申込は全て土の夜間に成立）
② その日に成立した申込を抽出し、プッシュ通知対象が確定
③ 募集人宛にプッシュ通知を発信
④ ネオnetの「新契約進捗状況照会」の進捗状況に反映
⑤ プッシュ通知を受け取り、ネオnetの「新契約進捗状況照会」を参照（この時点で進捗状況が成立になっている）

⸻

🔸 English:

① Applications marked as “Pending Confirmation” are finalized overnight.
(For weeks with holidays, applications marked on Friday/Saturday are all finalized Saturday night.)

② Applications finalized that day are extracted, and push notification targets are determined.

③ Push notifications are sent to the relevant agents (recruiters).

④ The progress status in ネオnet’s “New Contract Progress Inquiry” screen is updated.

⑤ Recipients check the push notification and confirm the finalized status via ネオnet’s progress screen.

